  audioSource: {fileID: 0}
  name: Bobson
  portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 6495d487ba8ef450caf11ef7620bff12, type: 3}
  morningDialogue: Up and at 'em early, huh? I guess that's the traveling merchant
    lifestyle for you.
  dayDialogue: Welcome to our quaint town. It ain't much, but we have some fine wood.
  eveningDialogue: Sometimes the paranoia sets in when you realize there are no women
    here or in any nearby town.
  nightDialogue: '*hic* A-ahm feelin'' good...'
